Students utilize tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database, enhancing participation and engagement. Monitors near the exit intermittently flash a link to a post-event survey, encouraging attendees to provide feedback. The dean also stops by to thank recruiters for supporting the university, fostering a sense of community. Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom.
